  - Atomically updates 32-bit readiness field (3 parts):
    - Lines 168-172: Bit layout (from most to least significant):
      - SHUTDOWN: 1 bit
      - TICK: 15 bits (version counter for clear)
      - READINESS: 16 bits (actual ready flags)
